        "mmx_texteditor": {
            "component_code": "mmx-text-editor",
            "item_code": "mmx_texteditor",
            "settings": {
                "_flex": {
                    "flex_version": 10.1103,
                    "settings_version": "10.11.03"
                },
                "content": {
                    "value": "<div class=\"charge-pipe-features\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"color: #004aad; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\">Sinister Diesel Cold Side Charge Pipes</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Features</h3>\r\n    <ul style=\"list-style: disc; margin-left: 20px;\">\r\n        <li><strong>6061 Aluminum Alloy Construction</strong> \u2013 Built for strength and longevity.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>CNC Mandrel Precision 3\" Tubing</strong> \u2013 Ensures a perfect fit and optimized airflow.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>5-Ply Silicone Boots Rated to 400 PSI</strong> \u2013 Maximum durability and reliability under extreme conditions.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Stainless Steel Spring Boot Clamps</strong> \u2013 Secure, leak-free seal for long-lasting performance.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Powder Coated in Signature Sinister Blue</strong> \u2013 A durable, polished finish for enhanced protection and style.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Higher Flow & Lower Turbulence Airflow</strong> \u2013 Improves power, throttle response, and turbo efficiency.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Made in the USA</strong> \u2013 Ensuring top-tier craftsmanship and quality control.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Benefits</h3>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Our Cold Side Charge Pipe is designed to optimize airflow, reduce turbo lag, and increase power and torque. The mandrel-bent tubing with smooth transitions minimizes turbulence and pressure drops, leading to improved throttle response and quicker spool-up times.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Built with high-quality materials, our charge pipes are engineered for long-lasting durability. The 5-ply silicone boots withstand up to 400 PSI, while the stainless steel clamps ensure a secure, leak-free fit.  \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        The Sinister Blue powder-coated finish not only enhances protection but adds a sleek, high-performance look to your engine bay. Unlike the factory plastic charge pipes, which are prone to failure, our aluminum construction provides the reliability and peace of mind that serious diesel owners demand.\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>"
                }
            }
        },
